{
  "stem": "5388.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He carried it with him in a postal card-- like a Russian postal card-- tied up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And you know, we had it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I don't know what happened to it-- misplaced.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "What a document that was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I-- I do remember the content.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was written with an [INAUDIBLE] type of pencil, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it-- it was written in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So father kind of felt like that was the end.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But then-- and that-- that transport left for Estonia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You want to go on further?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There's still some time there?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Just maybe-- if you feel up to it, the songs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a few songs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I will write it out for you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't have it written out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But one of them was-- you know, I'm not talking about the general songs in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's well known and people know them and so forth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But there were some songs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One of them was from the ghetto of Grodno about a Jewish policeman-- that he dreams about being at the gate.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The reason there's a gate-- because there is where the action is.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's where you can smuggle in some stuff and get a part of it if you work with somebody bringing in food from outside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he says that he is-- he is watching the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The cemetery was right smack in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so young couples-- where could they go in any place?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they used to go to the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That used to be their love nest to meet somebody.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I said-- so he says, I am watching the cemetery and-- where the young people don't give rest to the deceased.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I can only dream about the ghetto gates.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my shoes-- I'm pretty wearing out.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
